      <para id="id5919411"><emphasis effect="bold">LEARNING OUTCOME 1: </emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">HISTORICAL ENQUIRY</emphasis>The learner will be able to use enquiry skills to investigate the past and present.</para>
      <section id="id2456499">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id1170114003050">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id2551345">1.1 works with sources: records and organises information from a variety of sources; </para>
        <para id="id2448172">1.2 answers questions: uses information from sources to answer questions;</para>
        <para id="id1170117440885">1.3 communicates answers: communicates knowledge and understanding in a variety of ways. </para>
